                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep6-security/authenticator-get-user-check-credentials.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Here's the deal: if you return <code>null</code> from <code>getCredentials()</code>, authentication is
skipped. But if you return <em>anything</em> else, Symfony calls <code>getUser()</code>:</p>
