<h2 id="enter-checkcredentials">Enter checkCredentials() <a class="headerlink" href="authenticator-get-user-check-credentials#enter-checkcredentials" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>This is our chance to verify the user's password if they have one or do any other
last-second validation. Return <code>true</code> if you're happy and the user should be logged
in.</p>
