<h2 id="configuring-in-security-yml">Configuring in security.yml <a class="headerlink" href="authenticator-get-user-check-credentials#configuring-in-security-yml" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Finally, copy the service name and open <code>security.yml</code>. To activate the authenticator,
add a new key under your firewall called <code>guard</code>. Add <code>authenticators</code> below that,
new line, dash and paste the service name:</p>
