</p>
<p>Now, whenever the app is about to redirect us, Symfony will stop instead, and show us
the web debug toolbar for that request.</p>
<p>Go to <code>/login</code> again and login in with <code>weaverryan+1@gmail.com</code> and <code>iliketurtles</code>.
Check this out: we're <em>still</em> at <code>/login</code>: the request finished, but it did <em>not</em>
redirect us yet. And in the web debug toolbar, we <em>are</em> logged in as
<code>weaverryan+1@gmail.com</code>.</p>
<p>So authentication works, but there's some issue with storing our User in the session.
Fortunately, that's going to be really easy to fix.</p>

    
