	                                <p>Hey there!</p><p>One way or another, this error occurs when you try to load a form (LoginForm) through Symfony's form system, but the class (LoginForm) is not found! Make sure your LoginForm class lives in the "Form" directory and that you have a "use" statement for the LoginForm class *inside* your LoginFormAuthenticator class. One way or another, we have some missing use statement or namespace mis-match that is causing the issue.</p><p>Let me know if that helps!</p>
